record.title: DISMISSING ELECTION CONTEST RELATING TO OFFICE OF REPRESENTATIVE FROM 21ST CONGRESSIONAL DISTRICT OF FLORIDA

speaking.paragraph: Mr. Speaker, I ask unanimous consent for the immediate consideration in the House of the resolution (H. Res. 459) dismissing the election contest relating to the office of Representative from the Twenty-first Congressional District of Florida.

record.narrative: The Clerk read the title of the resolution.
record.chair: Is there objection to the request of the gentleman from Pennsylvania?
record.narrative: The Clerk read the resolution, as follows:
